annotationA: Lethal(2)neighbour of tid protein; Transferase activity, transferring hexosyl groups
annotationB: Putative Dol-P-Glc:Glc(2)Man(9)GlcNAc(2)-PP-Dol alpha-1,2-glucosyltransferase; Adds the third glucose residue to the lipid-linked oligosaccharide precursor for N-linked glycosylation.
